OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPerhaps the odd light shower
OL,6,Fover the Argyll Isles. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be a dry and bright day with some
OL,8,Fhazy sunny spells. Light winds.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FBright but partly cloudy this
OL,11,Fevening. Risk of a few showers for
OL,12,FArgyll through the evening and night,
OL,13,Fwhile the Glasgow area will stay
OL,14,Fmostly dry.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA bright morning with hazy
OL,17,Fsunny spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,18,Fdevelop through the day and bring a
OL,19,Ffew showers, some of which may be on
OL,20,Fthe heavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
